Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:14.14,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:26.88,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}さよならの想い出を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:33.79,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}瞳にたたえて　見つめる夢　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:39.04,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}壊れてしまう　うたかたのメモリー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:44.59,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}寂しさの涙　そっと拭こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:51.67,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}伸ばした手は観覧車　優しくとらえて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:56.92,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}目覚めそうな　記憶の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:02.85,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}うつむいて　消えてほしいと祈るけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:09.03,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}君が見つけてくれたこの声を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:16.11,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}動き出した時計の針　世界はやがて色づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:22.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}プラスティックな心が輝き出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:27.16,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}忘れないで　おぼえていて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:34.18,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}いつかまた巡り合える日まで
Comment: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:14.14,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}光芒聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:26.88,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}离别的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:33.79,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}溢满了眼眶 凝视不放的梦甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:39.04,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}早已支离破碎 如泡沫般的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:44.59,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}拭去寂寞的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:51.67,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}你的手如同摩天轮 温柔地带走我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:56.92,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}似乎就要回想起 残缺的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:02.85,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}可我却低头祈望记忆消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:09.03,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}你替我找到的 这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:16.11,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}时针开始旋转 世界渐渐染上色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:22.37,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}塑胶的心亦绽放光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:27.16,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不要忘记 请你记得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:34.18,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}直至再相会的那一天
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:24.47,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}はぐれた君を探してたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:28.19,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}呼びかけた声かき消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:36.14,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}僕が握りしめたその手は　震えていたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.97,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ふたりの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:45.01,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}戻せない時間抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:49.69,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}高く飛んでくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:54.28,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}万華鏡空にきらめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.11,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}君がぎこちなく微笑んでて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.09,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}愛しさ溢れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:08.83,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}光が溶けてくその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.94,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}心から願うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:24.30,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}この瞬間を　永遠に忘れないようにと
Comment: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:24.47,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在路上寻找你走散的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:28.19,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我呼唤的声响被风儿掠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:36.14,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}手中紧握的小手 不安的悸动着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.97,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你我彼此的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:45.01,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}紧抱着流逝的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:49.69,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}高高升起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:54.28,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}万花筒夜空中亦绽放虹彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.11,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你努力挤出僵硬的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.09,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}爱意满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:08.83,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在光晕染之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.94,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我自内心许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:24.30,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望能永远记住这一分一秒
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}SAI终端服务一般被称为回收方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在世界各地共有29个部门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我所就职的第一终端服务负责管辖总部所在的远东地区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这之后又要去总部开会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胃又疼起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉可以帮我泡杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}课长别老是把艾拉当作泡茶的使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在她可是司的执行者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请在这里签字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只不过是还没改掉习惯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟 诸位好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}縹康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的观测者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别看那样他可是在这里工作了快十年的老手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这小子 放着工作不做去哪里偷懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然是带薪休假或者出差什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来去女人那里叫做出差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还是第一次这样听说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记住这个绝不会吃亏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝君那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真棒 艾拉你泡的茶依然是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉组队的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我叫水柿司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那个啥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和伍堂部长打招呼 照顾进来的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说呀 你和部长是什么样的关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请一定要告诉我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为患了阑尾炎结果应试失败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有必要就不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感谢你的父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这次是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果我认为你并不适合在我们公司工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会立刻开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记住了吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}部长和我父亲认识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和你有点话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉~我的搭档呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 再多来点笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们这里的女孩子 为什么都表情这么可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是因为你这几天丢下工作不管的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于这个 还希望你可以充分的说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 但是我肚子有点饿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想先去吃点东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个笑话可真是好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要太紧张 放松点好好干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救命…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(417,417)\pos(768,613)\39\blur5\bord3\3c&H7A46F0&}#02   不想扯后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(417,417)\39\bord0.5\3c&H4C49B7&\pos(768,613)}#02   不想扯后腿
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是柳丰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们并不是可疑的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老实地将那边的马克思交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是终端服务 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}你们搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马克思快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂等等 为什么要吓唬他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 我没有听清楚 请再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之先追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呆着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被他们跑掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来又要写检讨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们先回去了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这都第几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三次…了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经给你安排相当轻松的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果三次都被拒签同意书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有好好和艾拉建立了信赖关系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应该不会变成这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毕竟是走后门的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不费一丝辛劳就进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 下次我会注意的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可恶 司那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能确实说的太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满总是直言不讳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说完又开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 你和司吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才没有那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘴上说着讨厌讨厌其实很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}清清纯纯的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 我和司才不是这种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都说了不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得和平时没什么两样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天下班后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有空的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你有在喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一开始就说我还未成年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说 你和艾拉有好好相处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不知道她在想什么」之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能告诉我关于艾拉的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月以前和艾拉是搭档吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告诉你也没有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果本人不去互相理解也是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也觉得很过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把她交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们这么多的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概也是因为艾拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然艾拉是个那样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可要好好和她相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜托你这种事我也是醉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我想和艾拉进一步搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这家伙是萝莉控吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老板再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}课长和总部总说要提高什么工作效率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就是胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也做了将近十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到现在也看不到正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁知道到底该如何销毁回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁都不会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何销毁回忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有在听吗 新人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香 香月小姐 好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耶 香月喝多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝先生怎么也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是这里的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这家伙喝了多少杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有三杯左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道说她酒量很差？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之我先送她回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经是常事了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 关门就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您辛苦了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs30\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\pos(674,261)\frx16\fry8}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs28\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\frx18\fry8\pos(584,457)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h单元测验房\N[训练]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}单元测验房？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是哪里
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 总部大楼里竟然还有这种设施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是艾拉的观测者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是终端服务部的专属工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是绘瑠 这位是铁黑右次郎师父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请跪拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无视我吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在采集数据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数据？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是在测量身体能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讨厌 居然偷看少女的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是个糟糕的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她经常会来做这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 只是和小司搭档之后才经常来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为最近负担也变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保养的次数也增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒希望她能休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}负担？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身体的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为以前就只是倒倒茶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而现在回到现场工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情况当然是不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别光动嘴不动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 对不起 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过看起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有点惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}擅自跑过来看 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么 我也没有躲藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么突然要训练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是在介意工作上的失误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时隔很久回到现场工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身体没能像想像中那样行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在的我在拖司的后退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是因为空档期的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很快就会找回感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 不只是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和持有者沟通的时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像立刻就会变得很僵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖…因为没有做暖机运转
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 暖机运转…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又不是以前的汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的需要吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要解决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作为你的执行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能再给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果司已经觉得受不了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就只能解散我们的搭档关系了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这人呢 其实很墨守成规的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作的话守规矩还是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以来这以后 我还是尽量试着读懂规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是相当的应付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「临机应变地对应」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「用最好的方法应对」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具体的内容一点都没写
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我能做的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}按照规则上写的临机应变地对应而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}临机应变？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如说 和持有者之间的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不让艾拉来做 而让我来做怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是观测者的工作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}监督搭档的执行者 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然我知道这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但好不容易能成为搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}互相帮助一下也挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在艾拉找回感觉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依靠一下我这种人也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要这样试一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就这样决定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就尽力来制定自己的规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…去下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 我下次会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 满
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 你觉得司这人怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才…才没有什么奇怪的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和司搭档是不是成为你的负担了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我感觉你最近很明显地在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不必对司这样的新人太客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不愿意的话就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你只是被课长强行和他组队的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且…拖后腿的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那家伙真是 果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呜嘎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然不向我如实汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不找借口才帅气」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你难道是这样想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说过那么多次不要再把自己当学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满 不要太生司的气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 首先是倾听对方的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是附和对方就能让人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司在问我一些奇怪的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和回收对象的所有者交涉时都需要注意些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么说 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底是无能还是蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这又怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提尔是有感情的 持有者也是有感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是从香月那里现学现卖来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听着 仅仅回收吉芙提尔是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则的话 我们的工作只能带来悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要依顺吉芙提尔和持有者双方的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}双方都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概只有我们这里会这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就连本部也对这种方法避而不用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 因为我是赞成香月的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以既然你来这里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就要实践这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了 谢谢你教给我这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 塞克 要去工作了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 现在就去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真的有那么要紧的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有 司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次对你说了很多过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满一大早就这么激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是到了复杂的年纪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我懂的 我家的女儿也是完全不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请别说那种令人悲伤的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 差不多就这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哟 真是努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉太会使唤人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在做自己用的工作手册
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么 比起我 艾拉更努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}单元测试房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了找回在空白期里丢失的感觉 每天都在进行训练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 不管能不能找回感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冒冒失失的样子大概是不会变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个孩子真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明知是徒劳却还是这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徒劳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉就是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是什么意思呢 徒劳什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…艾拉的身体测试数据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微瞥到过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是一直在下降？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 不是因此才为了弥补空白期而进行训练的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提尔和人类还有其他机器人一样要学习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 吉芙提尔并没有空白期的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们体内原本就没有植入遗忘功能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎样训练都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉以后一直会是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子自己也应该明白的才对
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是因为我太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才让她那么勉强自己的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:21:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢 我…会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都被她那样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}柳丰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是SAI公司的终端服务人员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是来通知您马克思的回收时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回收？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次让您受惊了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要回收了啊 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次逃走了真是抱歉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是司的报告书？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 他们两个意外的很合拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.29,0:23:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过还真是让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你居然什么都没跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别装了 你没和他说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉所剩的寿命还有2000小时的那件事
